TY  - JOUR
T1  - Existence of Optimal Mechanisms in Principal-Agent Problems
AU  - Kadan, Ohad
AU  - Reny, Philip J.
AU  - Swinkels, Jeroen M.
Y1  - 2017/05/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA12340
