TY  - JOUR
T1  - Generalized Instrumental Variable Models
AU  - Chesher, Andrew
AU  - Rosen, Adam M.
Y1  - 2017/05/01
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2017/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA12223
T2  - Econometrica
